column5: There was another incedent this weekend below the falls some one fell of a railed off area and may be charged under the niagra parks act.  http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20110814/man-falls-into-niagara-gorge-110814/20110814/?hub=TorontoNewHome
